# FILENAME  submitJobs_mumu.dag
#   SUBDAG of   submitSelection_mumu.dag
#   JOBS        submitRun.sub
#   SCRIPTS     runHadd.sh
#
# SUBMITS   mumu selection jobs for SingleMuon dataset and all MC samples
#           and combines output files for each run
#
# HARDCODED selection ("mumu"), sample names ($suffix), sample sizes ($nFiles)
#


JOB             muon_2016   submitRun.sub 

VARS            muon_2016   selection="mumu"
VARS            muon_2016   suffix="muon_2016"
VARS            muon_2016   nFiles="5"

SCRIPT  POST    muon_2016   runHadd.sh mumu muon_2016


